{"tid":13176,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"吃紅肉會致癌 玻利維亞政府：大家來吃林早洩","createTime":"2016-11-30T02:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T03:22:05.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"255bd1827d0d6ca549029ddb374c29dbe4ced52e","tid":13176,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/105645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F105645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ec2cd6f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界衞生組織日前將加工肉列為「一級致癌物」，紅肉也是2A級致癌物，而玻利維亞衞生部就建議，改吃羊駝肉(草泥馬肉)。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，玻利維亞衛生官員阿吉拉爾(Vicky Aguilar)表示，玻利維亞有優質肉，例如羊駝肉，脂肪比例低且內含豐富蛋白質，對身體好。不過他也提醒，任何食物如過吃過量，都對身體不好。玻利維亞原住民有吃羊駝肉習慣，過去當地高檔餐廳也有供應。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"9f7e6be1f7366d95cd9624d6f3be498ac6a51e76","tid":13176,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0b41ae3f827273d17f73eb9e80a3da4e30a546","tid":13176,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/105645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F105645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9e02f094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界衞生組織日前將加工肉列為「一級致癌物」，紅肉也是2A級致癌物，而玻利維亞衞生部就建議，改吃羊駝肉(草泥馬肉)。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，玻利維亞衛生官員阿吉拉爾(Vicky Aguilar)表示，玻利維亞有優質肉，例如羊駝肉，脂肪比例低且內含豐富蛋白質，對身體好。不過他也提醒，任何食物如過吃過量，都對身體不好。玻利維亞原住民有吃羊駝肉習慣，過去當地高檔餐廳也有供應。（<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">施旖婕</span></span>／綜合外電報導）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73ca10c85238eb2f409ab8f3a31ae29621c9fdf","tid":13176,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}